\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c193917 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c193917\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pricing<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a98d8d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a98d8d6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>HubSpot CRM offers a free tier with basic features suitable for small businesses. For more advanced needs, paid plans provide additional marketing, sales, and customer service tools.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-173002b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"173002b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/HubSpot-CRM-Pricing-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-17481\" alt=\"HubSpot CRM Pricing\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/HubSpot-CRM-Pricing-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/HubSpot-CRM-Pricing-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/HubSpot-CRM-Pricing-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/HubSpot-CRM-Pricing.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-wid